Volcanic Stove is a The Lion King themed piece of [[:Category:Cooking Stations|cooking station]] furniture.

It functions as a [[:Category:Cooking Stations|cooking station]], and once placed it can be interacted with to make [[Cooking|meal recipes]].


Once it is placed in the world, the Player can '''Interact''' with the object to toggle the fire on and off.


'''Mochi's Cat House''' is a [[Furniture#Big Hero 6|Big Hero 6]] themed piece of [[:Category:Companion Home|companion house]] [[furniture]].


It can be positioned and placed using the [[Furniture menu]] inside the [[Inventory]], and it can only be placed outdoors. Once it is placed in the world, the Player can '''Interact''' with the item to select up to 4 [[Companions|companions]]. These companions will roam in the immediate area and interact with nearby Companion items.


'''Cozy Companion Home''' is a [[Crafting#Functional_Items|functional item]] which can be [[Crafting|crafted]] using a [[:Category:Crafting_Stations|crafting station]].

'''Bayou Companion Home''' is a [[The Princess and the Frog]] themed piece of [[Crafting#Furniture|craftable furniture]] that can be made using a [[:Category:Crafting_Stations|crafting station]]. 


